object.customQuery:
with last_ten_year as(

    select * from cert_msgr.dim_date where  year_number>=EXTRACT(YEAR FROM DATEADD(year, -10, GETDATE()))
    )

select
    -- fact_msgr fields
    msgr.combined_key,
    msgr.claim_key,
    msgr.policy_key,
    msgr.policy_key_code,
    msgr.agency_key,
    msgr.coverage_key,
    msgr.major_peril_key,
    msgr.claim_transaction_key,
--    msgr.account_entered_dt ,
--    msgr.accident_dt,
--    msgr.reported_dt,
    msgr.claim_type,
    msgr.loss_cause,
    msgr.loss_cause_desc,
    msgr.sub_loss_cause_desc,
--    msgr.claim_paid_dt,
    msgr.datasource_name,
    msgr.risk_state_id,
    msgr.inforce_policy_key,
    msgr.loss_paid_amt,
    msgr.loss_paid_recovery_amt,
    msgr.loss_salvage_amt,
    msgr.loss_subrogation_amt,
    msgr.loss_ulae_expense,
    msgr.loss_alae_expense,
    msgr.loss_reserve_amt,
    msgr.loss_reserve_for_incurred_loss,
    msgr.incurred_loss_amt,
    msgr.loss_os_adj_exp,
    msgr.written_premium,
    msgr.commission_amount,
    msgr.taxes_service_charges,
    msgr.inforce_premium,
    msgr.earned_premium,
    msgr.unearned_premium,

    --dim_agency fields
    da.agency_code as agency_id,
    da.agency_group,
    da.agency_group_name,
    da.agency_name,
    da.agency_address,
    da.agency_city,
    da.agency_state,
    da.agency_city_state,
    da.field_representative as sales_territory,
    da.field_representative_group as sales_territory_group,
    da.agency_appointed_dt,
    da.agency_contact_phone,
    da.agency_alpha_workflow,

    -- dim_claims fields
    dc.claim_number,
    dc.claim_status,
    dc.cat_desc,
    dc.cat_group_desc,

    -- dim_coverage fields
    dco.coverage_limit1,
    dco.coverage_limit2,
    dco.coverage_limit3,
    dco.coverage_limit4,
    dco.coverage_desc,
    dco.coverage_deductible,

    -- dim_majorperil fields
    dm.majorperil_display as major_peril,

    -- dim_policy fields
    dp.policy_key as master_policy_key,
    dp.gw_policy_number as policy_number,
    dp.gw_policy_number,
    dp.customer_number,
    dp.company_desc,
    dp.source_cd,
    dp.renewal_code_desc as policy_status,
    dp.renewal_code_desc,
    dp.fairplan_desc,
    dp.lob_group_desc,
    dp.new_renewal_desc,
    dp.new_renewal_desc as new_renewal_indicator,
    dp.lob_desc,
    dp.insurance_score_desc,
    dp.insurance_score,
    dp.secondary_insurance_score_run_date,
    dp.secondary_insurance_score_run_year,
    dp.operator,
    dp.inexperienced_operator,
    dp.policy_inception_date,
    dp.policy_effective_date,
    dp.policy_expiration_date,
    dp.policy_transaction_dt,
    dp.pay_plan,
    dp.automatic_renewal,
    dp.policy_symbol,
    dp.module_number,
    dp.insured_name,
    dp.insured_address,
    dp.billing_type,
    dp.producer_code,
    dp.producer_name,
    dp.formatted_insured_address,

    -- dim_risk fields
    dr.policy_key_code_flag,
    dr.secondary_home_desc,
    dr.blanket_policy_ind,
    dr.cov_a_premium,
    dr.cov_c_premium,
    dr.building_limits_group,
    dr.building_limits,
    dr.building_limit_amt,
    dr.building_limit_band_1k,
    dr.building_limit_band_100k,
    dr.building_limit_band_500k,
    dr.contents_limit,
    dr.total_insured_value,
    dr.individual_risk_premium_mod,
    dr.expense_mod,
    dr.age_credit_amt,
    dr.dupc_credit_amt,
    dr.prc_credit,
    dr.latitude,
    dr.longitude,
    dr.wind_deductible_type,
    dr.wind_deductible_amt,
    dr.per_unit_deductible_type,
    dr.per_unit_deductible_amt,
    dr.distance_to_shore_feet,
    dr.distance_to_shore_mile,
    dr.sir_coastline_feet,
    dr.sir_coastline_mile,
    dr.flood_zone,
    dr.elevation,
    dr.class_code,
    dr.building_class_code,
    dr.contents_class_code,
    dr.construction_type,
    dr.construction_year,
    dr.construction_year_band,
    dr.contents_limits_group,
    dr.contents_limits,
    dr.form,
    dr.liability_limit,
    dr.commercial_liability_limit,
    dr.water_backup_limit,
    dr.number_of_apartments,
    dr.number_of_families,
    dr.occupancy,
    dr.protection_class,
    dr.sprinkler,
    dr.rating_territory,
    dr.rating_territory_desc,
    dr.risk_address,
    dr.risk_city,
    dr.risk_zip,
    dr.personal_umbrella_limit,
    dr.building_num,
    dr.building_status,
    dr.number_of_apartments_band,
    dr.total_num_of_units_in_complex,
    dr.number_of_stories,
    dr.number_of_stories_band,
    dr.sq_feet_area,
    dr.sq_feet_area_band,
    dr.deductible,
    dr.num_vehicles,
    dr.distance_to_shore_band,
    dr.sir_coastline_band,
    dr.num_buildings_complex,
    dr.building_class_description,
    dr.contents_class_description,
    dr.risk_county,
    dr.risk_state,
    dr.formatted_risk_address,
    dr.formatted_risk_city,
    dr.formatted_risk_zip,
    dr.formatted_risk_latitude,
    dr.formatted_risk_longitude,
    dr.elite_package_ind,
    dr.formatted_street,
    dr.formatted_county,

    --dim_date fields
    dd.full_date as account_entered_dt,
    dda.full_date as accident_dt,
    ddr.full_date as reported_dt,
    ddc.full_date as claim_paid_dt

from cert_msgr.fact_msgr msgr
inner join last_ten_year dd on msgr.account_entered_dt = dd.date_id
inner join cert_msgr.dim_risk dr on msgr.policy_key_code = dr.policy_key_code
inner join cert_msgr.dim_policy dp on msgr.policy_key = dp.policy_key
inner join cert_msgr.dim_coverage dco on msgr.coverage_key = dco.policy_coverage_code
inner join cert_msgr.dim_claims dc on msgr.claim_key = dc.claim_key
inner join cert_msgr.dim_date dda on msgr.accident_dt = dda.date_id
inner join cert_msgr.dim_date ddr on msgr.reported_dt = ddr.date_id
inner join cert_msgr.dim_date ddc on msgr.claim_paid_dt = ddc.date_id
inner join cert_msgr.dim_agency da on msgr.agency_key = da.agency_code
inner join cert_msgr.dim_majorperil dm on msgr.major_peril_key = dm.majorperil_cd
